new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Diff","Total_Confirmed_Diff","Daily_Recovered_Diff","Total_Recovered_Diff","Daily_Deceased_Diff","Total_Deceased_diff"]
pos_neg_dict={}
pos_neg_len_dict={}
a=[]
b=[]
for i,j in zip(kys,new_cols):
    pos=datajly_diff[datajly_diff[j]>0]
    a.append(pos)
    b.append(len(pos))
    neg=datajly_diff[datajly_diff[j]<0]
    a.append(neg)
    b.append(len(neg))
    zro=datajly_diff[datajly_diff[j]==0]
    a.append(zro)
    b.append(len(zro))
    pos_neg_dict.update({i:a})
    pos_neg_len_dict.update({i:b})
    a=[]
    b=[]
